{
  "video_id": "RVVR4QyiqMc",
  "title": "My Father, Stephen Hawking",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 9120.0,
      "end_time": 11520.0,
      "text": "This is my father, Stephen Hawking."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12340.0,
      "end_time": 14820.0,
      "text": "and it's a very nice photograph of him"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14820.0,
      "end_time": 16360.0,
      "text": "he's a very brilliant man"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 17440.0,
      "end_time": 19440.0,
      "text": "he's a theoretical phisicist"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20160.0,
      "end_time": 22560.0,
      "text": "and that means that he looks for ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22560.0,
      "end_time": 24720.0,
      "text": "to understand the universe around us"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24720.0,
      "end_time": 26480.0,
      "text": "using the laws of physics."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 26480.0,
      "end_time": 30680.0,
      "text": "And so he's a very brilliant man and he's the Lucasian professor of Mathematics at Cambridge University"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31640.0,
      "end_time": 36840.0,
      "text": "so that's a very long way to say it's the same job of the great scientist Isaac Newton once held"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37640.0,
      "end_time": 38140.0,
      "text": "And he's  won many awards and been given many honorary degrees"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38140.0,
      "end_time": 39320.0,
      "text": "And so you would think that this would have been obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39320.0,
      "end_time": 41320.0,
      "text": "right from the beginning"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44720.0,
      "end_time": 48640.0,
      "text": "Well this is the part of the talk where we do some time travel"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48800.0,
      "end_time": 51200.0,
      "text": "We're going to go back and take a look"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51680.0,
      "end_time": 52480.0,
      "text": "So here he is"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54240.0,
      "end_time": 57600.0,
      "text": "This is my father as a small boy with his two sisters"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57600.0,
      "end_time": 59520.0,
      "text": "And when my father was a young boy"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59920.0,
      "end_time": 64000.0,
      "text": "and he was at school his teachers didn't think that much of him"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64560.0,
      "end_time": 67440.0,
      "text": "This is a line from one of his school reports"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71060.0,
      "end_time": 72980.0,
      "text": "This boy will never amount to anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73280.0,
      "end_time": 77440.0,
      "text": "However his classmates must have noticed something about him"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77520.0,
      "end_time": 80000.0,
      "text": "Because they nicknamed him Einstein"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80320.0,
      "end_time": 82560.0,
      "text": "and he did go on to become a scholar"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82560.0,
      "end_time": 86400.0,
      "text": "And this just shows that kids are so much cleverer than adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86400.0,
      "end_time": 89600.0,
      "text": "Because he became a scholar and he went to Oxford University"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89840.0,
      "end_time": 92800.0,
      "text": "and he left with a first in honours in Physics"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92800.0,
      "end_time": 94080.0,
      "text": "and he came to Cambridge to begin his research"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95600.0,
      "end_time": 100480.0,
      "text": "Now around this time he also found out that he was suffering from a disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101120.0,
      "end_time": 103040.0,
      "text": "And it's a disease called ALS"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104000.0,
      "end_time": 106240.0,
      "text": "and what it does is it slowly takes"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106240.0,
      "end_time": 108800.0,
      "text": "away your ability to move your muscles"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109520.0,
      "end_time": 111360.0,
      "text": "and in later years it's also"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112120.0,
      "end_time": 114760.0,
      "text": "taken away his natural speaking voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115220.0,
      "end_time": 116480.0,
      "text": "And so at the end of the talk when you here him talking to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116480.0,
      "end_time": 119040.0,
      "text": "it will sound like a computer is speaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120080.0,
      "end_time": 122240.0,
      "text": "to you but it isn't it's a real man"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122240.0,
      "end_time": 128000.0,
      "text": "who's using a computer to give himself back the voice that his disease has taken away from him"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128000.0,
      "end_time": 132480.0,
      "text": "but fortunately some good things also happened to my father in this time"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132480.0,
      "end_time": 134400.0,
      "text": "he met my mother and he got engaged and he got married"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135020.0,
      "end_time": 137180.0,
      "text": "and he started work on his thesis"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137600.0,
      "end_time": 140160.0,
      "text": "and his thesis was called 'Properties of Expanding Universes'"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141120.0,
      "end_time": 144000.0,
      "text": "and as part of his thesis he managed to prove"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144000.0,
      "end_time": 147200.0,
      "text": "that the Universe must have had a definite beginning"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147200.0,
      "end_time": 149760.0,
      "text": "so that's not bad for a bit of post-graduate work actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150640.0,
      "end_time": 152960.0,
      "text": "and now a few years on and here we are"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153200.0,
      "end_time": 154880.0,
      "text": "this is 1970 in Cambridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154960.0,
      "end_time": 156160.0,
      "text": "and that baby is me"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157680.0,
      "end_time": 159360.0,
      "text": "and my parent's called me"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159360.0,
      "end_time": 162560.0,
      "text": "Lucy because the name 'Lucy' comes from the Latin"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162560.0,
      "end_time": 164060.0,
      "text": "word for light"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164060.0,
      "end_time": 167040.0,
      "text": "and light is one of the major studies of astrophysicists"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167040.0,
      "end_time": 168320.0,
      "text": "like my father and so"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168320.0,
      "end_time": 169600.0,
      "text": "it's a very good name"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 169600.0,
      "end_time": 171200.0,
      "text": "for the daughter of a physcist"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171360.0,
      "end_time": 174720.0,
      "text": "and the reason I'm showing you this photo from 1970"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174720.0,
      "end_time": 177280.0,
      "text": "1970 was an important year for my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 177280.0,
      "end_time": 178560.0,
      "text": "he had a Eureka moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178960.0,
      "end_time": 182400.0,
      "text": "and he worked out a very elegant mathematical proof"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182400.0,
      "end_time": 185360.0,
      "text": "of what happens when two black holes collide"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186400.0,
      "end_time": 189440.0,
      "text": "he worked out that when two black holes collide they join to form a larger black hole"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189680.0,
      "end_time": 191360.0,
      "text": "but that they can't split"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 191360.0,
      "end_time": 192640.0,
      "text": "to form two black holes"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 192640.0,
      "end_time": 194560.0,
      "text": "so as you can tell I was a very inspirational"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195040.0,
      "end_time": 197120.0,
      "text": "thought-provoking baby there"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 197120.0,
      "end_time": 197680.0,
      "text": "* laugh *"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 197680.0,
      "end_time": 199680.0,
      "text": "And here we are this is a few years later"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 199680.0,
      "end_time": 200960.0,
      "text": "and we have moved to CalTech"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200960.0,
      "end_time": 203500.0,
      "text": "we're now living in California in Pasadena"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 204880.0,
      "end_time": 207320.0,
      "text": "and Caltech is a great centre for scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 207320.0,
      "end_time": 209300.0,
      "text": "on the West Coast of America. And this is"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 209300.0,
      "end_time": 213040.0,
      "text": "1974 which was another very important year for my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213040.0,
      "end_time": 215800.0,
      "text": "because he's working on his realisations"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 215800.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "about what happens when a star implodes to form a"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217280.0,
      "end_time": 218340.0,
      "text": "black hole."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 218340.0,
      "end_time": 221100.0,
      "text": "So we saw the supernova the great explosion"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 221200.0,
      "end_time": 223200.0,
      "text": "at the end of a star's life a few"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 223200.0,
      "end_time": 225300.0,
      "text": "minutes ago and what happens if it"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 225300.0,
      "end_time": 228580.0,
      "text": "was a big enough star it throws the outer layers off"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229820.0,
      "end_time": 230960.0,
      "text": "and the inner core can collapse on itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 231340.0,
      "end_time": 233420.0,
      "text": "to form a black hole"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 233420.0,
      "end_time": 234600.0,
      "text": "And that's what my father's working on"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 235000.0,
      "end_time": 236080.0,
      "text": "at this point"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 236080.0,
      "end_time": 238660.0,
      "text": "now after this we go back to England and my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 238660.0,
      "end_time": 239900.0,
      "text": "takes up his professorship at Cambridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 239900.0,
      "end_time": 242120.0,
      "text": "and many many many things happen over"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 242200.0,
      "end_time": 244280.0,
      "text": "the intervening years I grew up"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 244940.0,
      "end_time": 246140.0,
      "text": "become a teenager"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 246600.0,
      "end_time": 249880.0,
      "text": "my school reports were really not so great either"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 250040.0,
      "end_time": 256560.0,
      "text": "* laugh *"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 256560.0,
      "end_time": 258220.0,
      "text": "And my father also has a very"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 258500.0,
      "end_time": 260340.0,
      "text": "very busy time he writes his"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 260339.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263080.0,
      "text": "best-selling work a Brief History of Time"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 263080.0,
      "end_time": 266180.0,
      "text": "now this is a book that has sold all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 267760.0,
      "end_time": 270940.0,
      "text": "and yet some people claim that not so many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 270940.0,
      "end_time": 271440.0,
      "text": "have actually managed to finish it."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 271600.0,
      "end_time": 274960.0,
      "text": "So that's one of the reasons why we set to work on our"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 274960.0,
      "end_time": 277960.0,
      "text": "children's books we set to work to try and add some extra"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 278140.0,
      "end_time": 279520.0,
      "text": "explanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 279520.0,
      "end_time": 281660.0,
      "text": "Now at that time my father also had some some"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 281660.0,
      "end_time": 284100.0,
      "text": "fun things going on in his life. He went on the Simpsons"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 284820.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "* laugh *"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289740.0,
      "text": "He really loved being on the Simpsons"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 289740.0,
      "end_time": 292800.0,
      "text": "the way they gave him helicopter blades for his wheelchair"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 292800.0,
      "end_time": 295220.0,
      "text": "but he did say that he's really glad that in real-life"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 295960.0,
      "end_time": 297480.0,
      "text": "he's not bright yellow"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 297740.0,
      "end_time": 298300.0,
      "text": "*laugh*"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 302500.0,
      "text": "He also did this he was on Star Trek"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 302900.0,
      "end_time": 306900.0,
      "text": "Paramount studios one day because he was working at Caltech"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 306900.0,
      "end_time": 308540.0,
      "text": "and they asked him if he'd like a part"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 308540.0,
      "end_time": 313160.0,
      "text": "and here he is on the enterprise with the two greatest scientist of all time."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 313160.0,
      "end_time": 315800.0,
      "text": "in my mind Isaac Newton and Albert Einstein"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 316220.0,
      "end_time": 319340.0,
      "text": "and a few more adventures here he is floating in"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 319340.0,
      "end_time": 322360.0,
      "text": "zero gravity. And this is a really lovely picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 322360.0,
      "end_time": 324480.0,
      "text": "because if you look at the size of his smile"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 325340.0,
      "end_time": 327420.0,
      "text": "and you think this is a man who's"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 327700.0,
      "end_time": 330020.0,
      "text": "mind has been free to travel across"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 330140.0,
      "end_time": 332780.0,
      "text": "the whole universe but his body has been and here he is he's free and he's floating."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 332780.0,
      "end_time": 335240.0,
      "text": "confined to a wheelchair for decades by this point"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 335660.0,
      "end_time": 339380.0,
      "text": "and here he is he's free and he's floating."
    }
  ]
}